  "text": "Pütün et al. [CITATION_1] have studied pyrolysis of cotton stalk for determining the main characteristics and quantities of liquid and solid products. Six inorganic compounds have been investigated by Jun et al. [CITATION_2] with regard to their catalytic effects on pyrolysis of three biomass species by thermal analysis experiments.",
